    "markdown": "## Portfolio Beta and Required Return\n\n\n\n\n\nAurora Technologies considers a portfolio of two divisions: Division A (β = **1.05**) with weight **53.4**% and Division B (β = **0.89**) with weight **46.6**%. The risk-free rate is **3**% and the expected market return is **9**%.\n\n::: {.question-block}\n\n<form onsubmit=\"event.preventDefault();\" style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:row;gap:6px;\">\n  <label for=\"module4_num_q15a\"><strong>1. What is the portfolio beta?</strong></label>\n  <input type=\"number\" id=\"module4_num_q15a\" name=\"module4_num_q15a\" placeholder=\"Enter value\" style=\"width:150px;\"\n    data-correct-answer=0.98 data-tolerance=\"0.01\"/>\n</form>\n\n<div id=\"feedback-module4_num_q15a\" class=\"feedback\" style=\"display:none;\">\n✅ Portfolio beta = w₁β₁ + w₂β₂ = **0.98**.\n</div>\n\n::: \n\n::: {.question-block}\n\n<form onsubmit=\"event.preventDefault();\" style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:row;gap:6px;\">\n  <label for=\"module4_num_q15b\"><strong>2. What is the required return of this portfolio (in %)?</strong></label>\n  <input type=\"number\" id=\"module4_num_q15b\" name=\"module4_num_q15b\" placeholder=\"Enter value\" style=\"width:150px;\"\n    data-correct-answer=8.85 data-tolerance=\"0.01\"/>\n</form>\n\n<div id=\"feedback-module4_num_q15b\" class=\"feedback\" style=\"display:none;\">\n✅ Required return = r_f + β_p (r_m − r_f) = **8.85**%.\n</div>\n\n::: \n",
